{"tid":2055963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【即日焦點】張曉明：「真普選」只會令社會分化　國安法助港走出困局；美國有團體促削警隊經費盼從根本改善治安","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T13:09:47.000Z","uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b61bebd625f2c09ff63302815a73e97f66babc5","tid":2055963,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】即日新聞焦點：<br />\n<br />\n【真正出路】張曉明：「真普選」只會令社會分化 國安法助港走出困局<br />\n<br />\n張曉明指，中央就港區國安法立法是理所當然、勢在必行，是香港的分離勢力及反對派迫使中央出手，強調國安法四大罪行與絕大多數港人無關。他又指香港目前主要面對政治問題，國安法有助香港走出困局，而「真普選」只會導致社會分化，不能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393721&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=c955b34f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393721&h=0a5f5340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393721</a>"},{"pid":"5de5e7ef416776d154dc15d7af9ec2daa595f503","tid":2055963,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"仲未死咩佢"},{"pid":"e9addbdd8528a0ded9d1582fdb798ba03acee16f","tid":2055963,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"張曉明係目前直接否定「真普選」既港澳體系最高級官員<br />\n代表中共終於正式推翻五大訴求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再上次有中共官員講真普選<br />\n已經係舊年9月既楊光<br />\n只係話&ldquo;香港的普選制度必須符合香港政治地位&quot; 無正式否定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190903/s00001/1567498033765/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6-%E6%99%AE%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%88%E7%AC%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25